                    <h4>Age Group</h4>
            <ul>
                        <li><a href="/web/20180712204200/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Aged%20%2865%20to%2079%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Aged%2B%2865%2Bto%2B79%2Byears%29">Aged (65 to 79 years)</a></li>                      
                        <li><a href="/web/20180712204200/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Middle%20Age%20%2845%20to%2064%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Middle%2BAge%2B%2845%2Bto%2B64%2Byears%29">Middle Age (45 to 64 years)</a></li>                      
                        <li><a href="/web/20180712204200/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Adult%20%2819%20to%2044%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Adult%2B%2819%2Bto%2B44%2Byears%29">Adult (19 to 44 years)</a></li>                      
                        <li><a href="/web/20180712204200/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Adolescent%20%2813%20to%2018%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Adolescent%2B%2813%2Bto%2B18%2Byears%29">Adolescent (13 to 18 years)</a></li>                      
            </ul>
                    <h4>UMLS Concepts <a href="/web/20180712204200/https://www.guideline.gov/help-and-about/search-browse/umls-concepts" class="what-is">(what is this?)</a></h4>
                <div class="field">
                    <h5 class="field-label">ICD9CM</h5>
                    <div class="field-content">
<a href="/web/20180712204200/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375137&amp;fLockTerm=Diabetes+with+neurological+manifestations%2c+type+II+or+unspecified+type%2c+not+stated+as+uncontrolled">Diabetes with neurological manifestations, type II or unspecified type, not stated as uncontrolled</a>
 (250.60), <a href="/web/20180712204200/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375134&amp;fLockTerm=Diabetes+with+ophthalmic+manifestations%2c+type+II+or+unspecified+type%2c+not+stated+as+uncontrolled">Diabetes with ophthalmic manifestations, type II or unspecified type, not stated as uncontrolled</a>
 (250.50), <a href="/web/20180712204200/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375141&amp;fLockTerm=Diabetes+with+peripheral+circulatory+disorders%2c+type+II+or+unspecified+type%2c+not+stated+as+uncontrolled">Diabetes with peripheral circulatory disorders, type II or unspecified type, not stated as uncontrolled</a>
 (250.70), <a href="/web/20180712204200/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375130&amp;fLockTerm=Diabetes+with+renal+manifestations%2c+type+II+or+unspecified+type%2c+not+stated+as+uncontrolled">Diabetes with renal manifestations, type II or unspecified type, not stated as uncontrolled</a>
 (250.40)                    </div>
