                        <h3><a href="#">Contraindications</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>Many routine medications used in type 2 diabetes mellitus are contraindicated during pregnancy. Refer to Appendix B in the original guideline document for additional information on contraindications to antidiabetic drugs.</p></div></p>

